<span style="font-size: 10pt;">4. The Russian-struck hotel, Odesa</span><br />
<span style="font-size: 10pt;">5. Velyka Oleksandrivka</span><br />
<span style="font-size: 10pt;">6. Posad-Pokrovske, occupied February–March, 2022</span><br />
<span style="font-size: 10pt;">7. Velyka Oleksandrivka</span><br />
