                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            Thomas, Tommy                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘We were forced into extreme proximity. Understandably, he found my behaviours insufferable.’<br><br>

Ralf Webb on friendship and loathing.                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                                        <a href="https://granta.com/cmon-billy/">
                            <div class="recommended-reads__item">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 recommended-reads__item-image_outer_container">
                                        <div class="recommended-reads__item__image-container">
                                            <img width="100" height="100" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20100%20100'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" data-lazy-src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Dead-Friendships7-100x100.jpeg" /><noscript><img width="100" height="100" src="https://granta.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Dead-Friendships7-100x100.jpeg" class="recommended-reads__item__image wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" /></noscript>                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10 col-md-8">
                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            C’mon Billy                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            ‘We weren’t fucking but we slept in the same bed, not out of necessity but out of a shared feeling that it would be inexcusable to waste even a second.’<br><br>

Lauren J. Joseph on friendships and fallouts.                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                            </div>
        
