            <div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
              <h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">William T. Vollmann</h1>
              <p class="article-contributor-section_content">William T. Vollmann’s books include <em>Europe Central</em>, <em>Imperial</em> and the <em>Seven Dreams: A Book of North American Landscapes</em> series. His forthcoming novel, <em>A Table for Fortune</em>, will appear in 2026.</p>
              <a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/william-t-vollmann">More about the author →</a>
